description: Deletes a security group. If you attempt to delete a security group that is associated with an instance or network interface, is referenced by another security group in the same VPC, or has a VPC association, the operation fails with DependencyViolation.

nested_items.name: Return
nested_items.description: Returns true if the request succeeds; otherwise, returns an error.

nested_items.name: GroupId
nested_items.description: The ID of the deleted security group.
